147909.name: Prevalence of anemia among women of reproductive age (% of women ages 15-49)
147909.description: Prevalence of anemia among women of reproductive age refers to the combined prevalence of both non-pregnant with haemoglobin levels below 12 g/dL and pregnant women with haemoglobin levels below 11 g/dL.
